{"tid":1417793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，認真想打贏場仗嘅全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:23.000Z","uid":267622,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22a768ad6d7dcc6f9a2664d182fa702c17070188","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:11:49.000Z","msg":"好多人睇完劉細良，話林鄭想用「<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span></span></strong>」frame成場黑衣革命，造成<span style=\"font-size: large;\">市民鬥市民</span>，令我哋雨傘咁失民心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拿，佢對林鄭/政府嘅判斷係好啱嘅。但至於驚驚豬要講明自己唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span>呢，我覺得係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戇鳩</span></strong>嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 咩先為之打贏場仗？我哋五大訴求逐個睇。  <br />\na)「撤回」係為乜？係堅決反對惡法呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真，唔只送中，國歌法國安法嗰啲都係一樣呀。點樣先唔使下下等佢想玩嘢先再動員？咪就係議會直選，光復議會囉！ <br />\nb) 咁獨立調查委員會呢？釋放所有義士呢？個委員會唔由直選嘅人查，唔通好似立會啲濕鳩委員會一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 釋放義士唔通唔使攞返合法權力，令律政司撤消檢控/逼特首特赦？ <br />\nc) 講到低，我哋唔<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重奪主權</span></strong></span>，算贏咩？最多留返個畀我哋打低嘅林鄭或者其他建制廢柴坐住特首個位先，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\">議會一定要重奪返嚟，行政權力同黑警權力一定要揼扁佢。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，大佬，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重奪主權</span></span></strong>呀喂，咁仲唔叫<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">革命</span></span>？當然，獨立嘅時機其實未成熟，我哋仲未組得成一個完整嘅新政府同國防軍，中共依家都仲未冧得住。但最少，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我哋要打冧個政府，形式上留返住佢個殼，實質上積蓄力量，建立我哋嘅自治秩序，以待未來嘅時機。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 好喇，竟然知道我哋嘅目標係咩，咁嚟緊要做咩？  唔好再用<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「爭取」</span></span>嘅心態諗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我哋唔只係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「施壓」</span></span>，施壓即係好似小朋友搞好多嘢出嚟，攪到個家長煩到唔理你都唔得。大佬呀，林鄭係向北京交代，唔係向香港人交代㗎。家長要理個細佬係因為有血緣有愛，我哋同林鄭冇血緣冇愛㗎。 唔用「施壓」角度，咁用咩角度？係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">「重奪」</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（其實我想用另一個term，不過少少驚入罪，自己諗係咩）<br />\n我哋要攞返嚟嘅，就要用自己對手去攞返嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好淨係諗住靠政府開個委員會查黑警，有撚用咩，我哋自己就要調查！我哋自己就要行使公民逮捕權，將班冇委任嘅冒警人士拉哂佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算好似黃大仙咁，屌到佢哋收隊又點？第日咪再出返嚟，著套靚靚gear射鳩你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔拉咗佢哋有咩用？另一方面，我哋自己就要搵班有民意授權嘅人，由民間成立調查委員會去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清算</span></strong></span>佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。拿，針對警暴呢點其實劉細良都同意㗎，不過佢嘅思維有慣性，諗唔到咁盡喳嘛。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 咁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民意</span>點算？我哋想做好多嘢，但民意逆轉點算？首先分清楚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幾塊民意</span>：1)<span style=\"color: red;\">hardcore抗爭者</span> 2<span style=\"color: orange;\">)淺黃支持者</span> 3)<span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍</span> 4)<span style=\"color: navy;\">深藍</span>。4)同1)都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔會變㗎喇</span>，唔使理。人最多嘅係<span style=\"color: orange;\">淺黃</span>同<span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍</span>。但講真，<span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍</span>其實行動力好低，佢哋最重視就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原有嘅秩序</span>，但秩序被破壞咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢哋最多都係鬧下你</span>。睇下你自己啲淺藍老竇老母，佢哋會唔會去撐警集會？我相信九成都唔會，佢哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政治冷感</span>㗎嘛。就算依家說服唔到佢哋，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">只要我哋贏咗，建立新秩序，佢哋就會乖乖接受。唔好考慮佢哋太多。</span></strong></span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: orange;\">淺黃</span>呢？個個見到嘩暴力好恐怖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點算？第一，我哋要繼續強調警暴，表示抗爭者係用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">合理武力反抗</span></span>。第二，我哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔可以淨係破壞、擾亂</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要建立自己嘅秩序，描繪自己嘅未來同希望。慢慢將佢哋嘅底線都拉高，帶埋佢哋一齊光復香港。 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 咁講完呢啲嘢，係咪繼續街頭見？講真，今日都就嚟拉到200人，咁落去真係好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個個最勇嘅都入哂去坐，唔掂喎。be water又唔早啲撤，撚狗撚得再開心，最尾又係畀人衝出嚟拉一堆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係話唔搞街頭抗爭，只不過係我哋要留意<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成本同成效</span>。  <br />\n<br />\n如果我哋要做嘅係建<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">立新秩序，積累香港自主嘅力量，光復香港</span>，日日同狗打，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">最早消耗完嘅一定係我哋。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知企前線、撚狗個感覺係好好，但我哋係時候要諗清楚我哋嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的</span>係咩，我哋要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做啲咩先可以提出一個未來同希望，實質上光復香港</span></strong></span>。  <br />\n<br />\n我哋除咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武鬥</span>，都要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文鬥</span>。如果我哋要針對警暴咬住唔放，我哋而家就要成<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立自己嘅獨立調查委員會</span></strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人邊度搵？儲齊一班議員，民意授權一定夠。咁搜證點算？連登仔起底最叻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉唔拉到人都唔係最重要，甚至夠唔夠證據都唔係最重要。我哋要向市民抌出一個籌碼，同佢講，我哋連委員會都成立咗喇，政府唔做我哋做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋依家就要非政府咁<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">通輯</span></span>呢班人，全港流傳通輯名單，嚇到班黑警瀨尿，令佢哋成為過街老鼠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後我哋要用民意授權，組成社區自衛隊，對發動恐襲嘅黑社會、冇委任證嘅懷疑冒警人士實行<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">公民逮捕令</span></span>，拉去公民監獄。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經濟方面，我哋唔只係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷工罷市</span>，我哋要自己組成一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支援抗爭嘅生產&mdash;&mdash;消費鏈</strong></span></span>。而家就有巴絲整理緊全港良心舖頭網絡。我哋一方面要喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">平時淨係支持良心舖頭</span>。另一方面，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全港罷稅，然後將啲錢組成一個抗爭者嘅公民央行</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />未來嘅定期罷工罷市，其實唔只係咩都唔做，而係攞啲公民稅去支持呢嘅店家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等佢哋為抗爭者提供物資、提供飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當我哋癱瘓咗香港嘅正常秩序，重建自己嘅秩序，我哋一方就會好似滾雪球咁愈嚟愈強，港共就會愈嚟愈弱。最尾唔理佢點反應，我哋都喺事實上贏咗。  </span><br />\n<br />\n最後，重覆返一句。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"79bcf25c57e54ed3d9df4ec862915492cbdae02f","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"11f992530e9c97bee18b22afc6be2921c36735dd","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"112387b1c29aacae9c4fa45708c0a0722048d5e2","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"係咪深度文就冇人睇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算插下都好吖 P牌我都唔想㗎"},{"pid":"87a748f9f240677e38244364a0a8ac1dd7dc79a8","tid":1417793,"uid":277835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eda234360a80c940b2ac7e1591657d1bd49cd460","tid":1417793,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"字體大細一樣<br />\n分段加標題<br />\n少啲顏色<br />\n出過ok?"},{"pid":"215720238ec822523856fc8f95d9928be0ceca99","tid":1417793,"uid":27312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"112387b1c29aacae9c4fa45708c0a0722048d5e2","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"係咪深度文就冇人睇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算插下都好吖 P牌我都唔想㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:43.000Z","msg":"宜家呢個時勢，大家都冇心機睇太長既野，唔洗灰心，精簡下再出post"},{"pid":"fc82edb7f19f1145012ed070873e1c844f6420e2","tid":1417793,"uid":249108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:50.000Z","msg":"民間獨立調查委員會點做 有啲黑警連自己個樣都遮埋"},{"pid":"434c6abab3830675da6cbb134e109b0805a43cc2","tid":1417793,"uid":267622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"sor9 太少出po 即刻出過"}]}